description: DeepSeek R1 architectural innovations and model design improvements

diagrams.code:
direction right
// Title
title Architectural Innovation Process

// Groups and nodes
Market Insights [shape: oval, icon: globe, color: lightblue]
Technology Advances [shape: oval, icon: cpu, color: lightblue]

Ideation Phase [color: orange, icon: lightbulb] {
  Gather Requirements [shape: rectangle, icon: search, color: orange]
  Generate Concepts [shape: rectangle, icon: lightbulb, color: orange]
  Select Promising Ideas [shape: diamond, icon: check-square, color: orange]
}

Design Phase [color: green] {
  Develop Digital Models [shape: rectangle, icon: box, color: green]
  Conduct Feasibility Analysis [shape: diamond, icon: activity, color: green]
  Refine Design [shape: rectangle, icon: edit-2, color: green]
}

Prototyping Phase [color: purple, icon: package] {
  Build Prototype [shape: rectangle, icon: package, color: purple]
  Test Prototype [shape: diamond, icon: activity, color: purple]
  Evaluate Performance [shape: rectangle, icon: bar-chart-2, color: purple]
}

Implementation Phase [color: blue, icon: send] {
  Finalize Documentation [shape: rectangle, icon: file-text, color: blue]
  Deploy Solution [shape: rectangle, icon: server, color: blue]
  Monitor Feedback [shape: diamond, icon: smile, color: blue]
}

End of Innovation [shape: oval, icon: flag, color: lightgreen]

// Relationships
Market Insights > Gather Requirements
Technology Advances > Gather Requirements
Gather Requirements > Generate Concepts
Select Promising Ideas > Develop Digital Models: Yes [color: green]
Select Promising Ideas > Generate Concepts: No [color: red]
Conduct Feasibility Analysis > Refine Design: Yes [color: green]
Conduct Feasibility Analysis > Develop Digital Models: No [color: red]
Refine Design > Build Prototype
Test Prototype > Evaluate Performance: Yes [color: green]
Test Prototype > Build Prototype: No [color: red]
Evaluate Performance > Finalize Documentation
Finalize Documentation > Deploy Solution
Deploy Solution > Monitor Feedback
Monitor Feedback > End of Innovation
